{"tid":1438143,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"支持成立獨立調查委員會？ 恒大校長：三個字","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T12:59:32.000Z","uid":87100,"like":497,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"06f55e8ff7647a4e0f952ff4ea526ada1e1a6861","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"<strong>支持成立獨立調查委員會？ 校長：三個字，Yes, I support. </strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n          校長指自己以往很少就政治申明立場，因他認為校長其中一個作用為保證校園內的言論自由，請同學諒解自己未能表達個人意見，然而今次的事件特別，亦令他焦慮不安。對於會長的問題，校長指之前就曾有學生直接去信向他提問，是否支持成立獨立調查委員會。校長則以一句 &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\"> Yes, I support</span>.&rdquo; 作回應。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>撤回修例有利情況 望特首特赦被捕者</strong><br />\n<br />\n      校長先表示認同撤回修例的訴求，認為對事情有幫助，「見到林鄭都會咁同佢講。」校長亦同意成立獨立調查委員會，指其能成為日後的歷史真相，「<span style=\"color: red;\">高官亦當然要查，不只限於警察</span>。」而對釋放被捕人士的訴求，校長表示到法律層面自己未能談及太多，亦未知特首是否有所權力，但他希望特首能夠運用權力特赦學生、被捕者，用最大的誠意去挽回誠信。<br />\n<br />\n      對最後兩個訴求，即撤回暴動定性及實現真普選，校長指法例本身對暴動的定義並不明確，但相信若獨立調查委員會能夠成立，是否暴動亦能查明清楚。校長亦直言真普選應該一直都是香港人爭取的目標，其本來就是《基本法》對港人的承諾，亦是當年<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">痕大利用完政府升格做私大之後，真係完全唔撚驚㗎喎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"3a6c1eb4fc33e533cc83654a13901b06a7228ab0","tid":1438143,"uid":94834,"like":228,"dislike":0,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"由今日開始恆大係大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c671daf56250a772c74e21f89c6218bb8bf163","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":98,"dislike":0,"score":98,"quote":{"pid":"3a6c1eb4fc33e533cc83654a13901b06a7228ab0","tid":1438143,"uid":94834,"like":228,"dislike":0,"score":228,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:52:46.000Z","msg":"由今日開始恆大係大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:56:25.000Z","msg":"以後叫恒大有落唔撚驚喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5718ca166dc5120eb6c939955b58219f5d5542","tid":1438143,"uid":147292,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"三大在我腳下"},{"pid":"19b22bb9db3bebd5319ac6c81835fdb3e3bb7558","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"9d5718ca166dc5120eb6c939955b58219f5d5542","tid":1438143,"uid":147292,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"三大在我腳下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"我以後唔會再笑Pound of my school<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfcf97185d9f5eb5efdb1960e7fcdff8e99ba26","tid":1438143,"uid":208017,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"我恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a3d9172d1982cee82bcbf0ef986106fe780cae","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1dfcf97185d9f5eb5efdb1960e7fcdff8e99ba26","tid":1438143,"uid":208017,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:02:36.000Z","msg":"我恆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就係要呢啲.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f19f82cdee6ae91152e4225d0d56f414bddba2","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa43040fa1229230500b8bb39b88d8a2de78d87","tid":1438143,"uid":58841,