焦點啦，你要屌就出post屌哂全部人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家個post講緊痕大校長正面回應學生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:43:29.000Z","msg":"個問題本身就係錯 <br />\n問校長同唔同意成立獨立委員會黎做乜柒<br />\n校長緊係支持啦<br />\n因為獨立調查委員會係維穩作用<br />\n完全無實際檢控嘅用途<br />\n樓豬條仆街仲吹奏個校長 吹奏獨立調查<br />\n好多無思考能力嘅人會覺得成立獨立調查係有用<br />\n宜家唔屌佢地 係咪等運動俾獨立調查搞散先屌呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e89e43833b4e52e21328d3e1eab0203994f22b1","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f04a2f9d3e4adace8926f3266453cb1a86dbc05b","tid":1438143,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"Source都唔貼你話佢話香港獨立都得架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:45:37.000Z","msg":"梳巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少出post唔知規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/451516261637371/posts/2203828076406172?s=735714987&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F451516261637371%2Fposts%2F2203828076406172%3Fs%3D735714987%26sfns%3Dmo&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=c52a9f35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/451516261637371/posts/2203828076406172?s=735714987&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"9fac1b6c336ae9badf27af95d21ea86734ea4bb2","tid":1438143,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1e89e43833b4e52e21328d3e1eab0203994f22b1","tid":1438143,"uid":87100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f04a2f9d3e4adace8926f3266453cb1a86dbc05b","tid":1438143,"uid":155710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"Source都唔貼你話佢話香港獨立都得架啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:45:37.000Z","msg":"梳巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />少出post唔知規矩<img src=\"/ass